{"word":"κολακεύω","slug":"κολακεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κολακεύω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κόλαξ'><el>κόλαξ</el></a>\n<p/><i>to flatter</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be flattered, be open to flattery</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}